We just made the sending experience a bit more easier and comfortable, thanks to your valuable feedback

* Pay instantly for your transaction with your UAE bank account (select banks)
* Transaction History now shows all remittance transactions done through any of our channels
* Now get more value for your transfer with our Promo Codes

Also we have resolved a few bugs which caused login issues, let the feedback keep coming, and lets build this app together to make your experience even more delightful.
